37:59.132 --> 38:00.764
Okay, okay. So I shouldn't have
told you, just don't start.

38:00.800 --> 38:03.266
This-this is the reality
of health care today.

38:03.302 --> 38:05.300
We'll fight it when necessary,

38:05.335 --> 38:07.472
we'll accommodate when possible,

38:07.509 --> 38:10.273
and we'll deal with it to survive.

38:10.309 --> 38:12.231
Barrett.

38:12.300 --> 38:15.085
I would like you to meet our
very best orthopedic surgeon

38:15.119 --> 38:17.581
and my good friend, Dr. Kit Voss.

38:17.617 --> 38:19.416
I'm glad to finally meet you.

38:19.452 --> 38:21.152
What you pulled off... saving a child

38:21.186 --> 38:22.920
who suffered an internal decapitation...

38:22.956 --> 38:25.956
- that was miraculous.
- Oh, thank you.

38:25.958 --> 38:28.460
Flattery will get you everywhere...

38:28.485 --> 38:30.918
with anyone but me.

38:36.802 --> 38:38.135
A word, Randolph.

38:38.170 --> 38:39.670
- When you get a minute.
- Absolutely.

38:39.706 --> 38:41.371
Pleasure.

38:45.311 --> 38:46.710
Why'd you do that?

38:46.746 --> 38:50.119
W-What is the point
of alienating the man?

38:50.153 --> 38:52.889
What is the point of making nice
when I know who he is?

38:52.925 --> 38:54.885
I am still trying to wrap my head

38:54.920 --> 38:56.521
around the fact that you hired someone

38:56.556 --> 38:58.556
who so obviously has an ego
the size of Texas.

38:58.590 --> 39:00.358
I... Red Rock Mountain Medical hired him,

39:00.393 --> 39:02.126
and I understand why they did.

39:02.161 --> 39:04.023
Health care is a business. I'm a realist.

39:04.059 --> 39:06.130
This is what's happening
from coast to coast.

39:06.166 --> 39:09.000
They're recruiting guys
like Cain. It's everywhere.

39:09.034 --> 39:11.001
And doctors like me,
who put our patients first,

39:11.036 --> 39:12.570
- are collateral damage.
- No.

39:12.605 --> 39:14.862
I'll start interviewing
elsewhere immediately.

39:14.898 --> 39:17.809
- No. K-Kit. Please, don't. Don't.
- I'm sorry.

39:17.844 --> 39:20.110
But I don't belong here.

39:28.054 --> 39:29.818
I see your, uh, your companion left.

39:29.853 --> 39:32.322
- Yeah.
- You know what, I don't want you

39:32.358 --> 39:33.865
