39:43.235 --> 39:44.931
I'm telling you, Randolph, stick with me

39:44.967 --> 39:46.534
and we'll rise together.

39:47.106 --> 39:49.474
The sky's the limit for men like us.

39:54.146 --> 39:56.146
Ladies, thank you for coming.

