40:36.623 --> 40:38.322
This isn't about a lawsuit.

40:38.358 --> 40:40.858
I gave that up.

40:43.596 --> 40:45.663
I just want the truth.

40:46.452 --> 40:48.085
I must have the truth.

40:49.335 --> 40:51.224
For Jessie.

41:01.047 --> 41:02.280
Mwah.

41:02.315 --> 41:04.481
Think I'm ready.

41:14.126 --> 41:15.425
CONRAD: I know.

41:15.460 --> 41:20.231
♪ Peace will find the restless ones ♪

41:23.001 --> 41:25.969
